18:31.482 --> 18:34.524
I fell down, uh, the--
the impact knocked me back

18:34.607 --> 18:35.899
and, uh...

18:35.982 --> 18:39.482
the, uh, projectile went
into the end of my flashlight,

18:39.565 --> 18:42.232
which is a Kel-Lite,
the big metal one,

18:42.315 --> 18:44.774
and, uh, it went through
several batteries

18:44.857 --> 18:47.524
and lodged in the back portion
of the flashlight.

18:51.107 --> 18:54.440
MICHELLE: The Ransacker struck
as many as 130 times

18:54.524 --> 18:57.649
over a period
of less than two years.

18:57.732 --> 19:01.273
But once the composite sketch
based on Bill McGowen's run-in

19:01.357 --> 19:04.607
with the Ransacker
was released to local press,

19:04.691 --> 19:07.857
he never struck Visalia again.

19:09.023 --> 19:11.816
The EAR series began
in Sacramento

19:11.899 --> 19:14.232
just six months later.

