and they said,

19:59.399 --> 20:00.607
"Yeah, that's the guy I saw."

20:00.691 --> 20:02.107
So, it kind of gives
further credence

20:02.190 --> 20:04.399
-this was the Ransacker.
-MICHELLE: I see. I see.

20:04.482 --> 20:06.649
HOLES:
Now, the very first EAR

20:06.732 --> 20:09.357
