20:13.107 --> 20:15.232
Broad-shouldered,
well-proportioned,

20:15.315 --> 20:16.440
but slim.

20:16.524 --> 20:20.190
So, six months
after Visalia Ransacker,

20:20.273 --> 20:23.732
-and now he's a skinny guy?
-MICHELLE: Mm-hmm.  (LAUGHS)

20:27.565 --> 20:31.440
