20:39.190 --> 20:40.565
born between these years

20:40.649 --> 20:42.607
who have connections
to these towns,

20:42.691 --> 20:44.899
so really it is
kind of just get--

20:44.982 --> 20:47.023
winnowing it down, you know.

20:49.524 --> 20:51.857
