20:55.065 --> 20:56.232
What about real estate?

20:56.315 --> 20:57.941
Will you be surprised
if he doesn't have a record?

20:58.023 --> 20:59.232
MAN: I will.

20:59.315 --> 21:01.107
MICHELLE: Do you feel like
