in Vietnam,

21:07.107 --> 21:08.899
so I, you know, I'm not sure
he wasn't a vet

21:08.982 --> 21:11.065
-or something like that.
-MAN: Right. Wow.

21:11.148 --> 21:12.565
MICHELLE: Yeah.

21:12.649 --> 21:14.065
One of the, um, things

21:14.148 --> 21:17.065
that the rape victims tell me
that he did a couple times

21:17.148 --> 21:18.774
