MICHELLE: The killer's
last known victim

29:29.440 --> 29:32.273
was an 18-year-old young woman
in Irvine

29:32.357 --> 29:34.440
named Janelle Cruz.

29:35.649 --> 29:37.816
That was in 1986.

29:49.857 --> 29:53.023
MICHELLE: Yeah.
It's hard to figure out.

29:56.065 --> 30:00.857
MELANIE: The Janelle Cruz case
was very interesting to us.

30:01.607 --> 30:03.273
You know, being 18 years old

30:03.357 --> 30:06.565
and just so innocent
and so young.

30:07.899 --> 30:09.941
WOMAN: Janelle!

30:10.023 --> 30:11.899
MICHELLE: She-- You know,
I was a teenager

30:11.982 --> 30:14.107
