-WOMAN: Say something!

30:14.190 --> 30:17.273
And I-- I'd just-- even looking
at her hairstyles and stuff,

30:17.357 --> 30:18.941
it's very familiar to me.

30:19.691 --> 30:22.148
MAN: Walk to me, Janelle.

30:22.232 --> 30:24.190
MICHELLE: The brief life
of Janelle Cruz

30:24.273 --> 30:26.607
was no less tragic
than her death.

30:28.065 --> 30:31.440
Her biological father
was long out of the picture.

30:31.524 --> 30:35.357
When she was 15,
she was drugged and raped.

30:35.440 --> 30:37.899
The crime went unreported.

30:41.524 --> 30:45.816
On May 3rd, 1986,
her mother and stepfather

30:45.899 --> 30:48.399
left for a vacation to Cancun.

30:49.482 --> 30:52.107
The following evening,
a teenage coworker

30:52.190 --> 30:54.357
hung out with Janelle
after she told him

30:54.440 --> 30:57.232
she was lonely
with her parents out of town.

30:59.941 --> 31:02.315
A noise outside startled them.

31:03.941 --> 31:07.107
Janelle looked out her window
and closed the shutters.

31:08.482 --> 31:10.148
"I think it's just the cats."

31:12.691 --> 31:15.774
The workmate left
a short time later.

31:19.774 --> 31:21.440
HOLES:
In the Janelle Cruz case,

31:21.524 --> 31:24.941
relative to the previous cases,
there's a lot of similarities.

31:29.732 --> 31:31.357
And it appears that he,
of course,

31:31.440 --> 31:33.023
is going through the backyard.

31:33.107 --> 31:35.857
He picked up the weapon,
likely a monkey wrench

31:35.941 --> 31:38.649
that was present
in the backyard.

31:38.732 --> 31:40.774
He's able to get inside...

31:43.565 --> 31:47.315
and then he binds her up
and she's raped

31:47.399 --> 31:49.107
and then she's bludgeoned.

31:50.315 --> 31:53.982
♪ (SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

31:59.440 --> 32:01.232
It's important to point out

32:01.315 --> 32:03.524
that when he attacks
Janelle Cruz,

32:03.607 --> 32:06.357
the Golden State Killer's
previous attack

32:06.440 --> 32:08.607
was five years earlier

32:08.691 --> 32:10.774
in July of 1981.

32:11.816 --> 32:17.107
♪ (DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

