Have you seen the,
um, the interview

33:36.315 --> 33:38.232
that-- with Janelle's mom?

33:38.315 --> 33:40.899
I mean, she kind of talks,
stream of consciousness

33:40.982 --> 33:42.232
in a way that I thought,

33:42.315 --> 33:44.899
"Someone who is an investigator
